answer: The main page for Novartis quarterly financial results is `https://www.novartis.com/investors/financial-data/quarterly-results/`. While this page provides links to individual quarter reports (e.g., Q3 2025, Q2 2025, Q1 2025, Q4 2024 releases), the "collection by release date and quarter" as a single navigable list is not explicitly presented on this page. It leads to specific reports or transcripts, but not for all 2024 quarters in a unified, filtered manner.
